{"tid":2232897,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【剝奪教育權利終身】被除牌教師不能進入任何學校","createTime":"2020-10-06T16:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T17:18:13.000Z","uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59136acf578d6a6dfb8186d58c0e75e5d523d0f4","tid":2232897,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:44:32.000Z","msg":"【被除牌教師不能進入任何學校】<br />\n【教育局：保障學生安全環境下學習】<br />\n<br />\n九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被取消註冊，教育局表示將不容許有關教師進入校園。本台向教育局查詢，「不容許有關教師進入校園」的定義為何，舉例問到，是否將來該名教師不能出席子女學校的家長會，甚至不允許參與校方一切活動。<br />\n<br />\n教育局回覆指，根據《教育條例》，任何人曾獲註冊為教員，其後被取消的人士，未經教育局常任秘書長書面准許，不得進入或逗留在任何學校，以保障學生在安全的環境下學習，日後如有需要進入任何學校，需要以書面向常任秘書長提出申請。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #港台電視31 #港台電視32 #十點半新聞天地 #九龍塘宣道小學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/738915030/posts/10160538579125031/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F738915030%2Fposts%2F10160538579125031%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=8c6b9b0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/738915030/posts/10160538579125031/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"36f5eaa6728906c74ed12ff7fe259c2ed7e2e253","tid":2232897,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b1f7c0b64fcfdd51245b7f6318419a30d51234","tid":2232897,"uid":185854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f65d5a9aa3f5f4e3e2f534042c7295b1fd302f","tid":2232897,"uid":65790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T16:50:09.000Z","msg":"見家長都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0e8949902670076b89e86a91f9402785f8309c","tid":2232897,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"scor